data.description: Here in the popular neighborhood of Prescott Country Club, lies a classic 3 bed, 2 bath contemporary home. Upon entrance you are warmly greeted by an open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the kitchen, living room, and Arizona room leading to the inviting sunny backyard. With low maintenance landscaping in the front yard as well as the back, this home offers just over 1,500 sqft. A very spacious master bedroom with a walk in closet, alongside 2 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, come see the home of your dreams!
